  Description: "Modifies the spell\u2019s behavior depending on the equipped Cast
    Rune. Each equipped rune adds it\xB4s effect up to 3. \r\n\r\nProjectile Cast
    - Your projectiles pierce through enemies. \r\n\r\nDash Cast - Dash through enemies
    to damage them. \r\n\r\nShield Cast - Your shield becomes a damage zone for enemies,
    but it now only blocks projectiles. "
